# This directory stores runtime databases (anomalies.db, baseline.db) and GeoLite2.
# These files are excluded from version control (.gitignore).
# After cloning:
#   1. Run: python launcher/baseline.py   (as Administrator) to generate baseline.db
#   2. The anomalies.db is created automatically on first scan.
#   3. Download GeoLite2-Country.mmdb from MaxMind and place it here (optional).
